2025-07-03PMOSalaries ActOrder Designating the Department of Industry to Provide Support to the Minister of Artificial Intelligence and Digital InnovationOrder designating the Department of Industry in order to (1) repeal Order in Council P.C. 2025-481 of May 13, 2025; and (2) provide support to the Minister of Artificial Intelligence and Digital Innovation in the carrying out of that Minister's responsibilities.Registration: SI/2025-0091 Publication Date: 2025-07-16
subject: Order Designating the Department of Industry to Provide Support to the Minister of Artificial Intelligence and Digital Innovation
precis: Order designating the Department of Industry in order to (1) repeal Order in Council P.C. 2025-481 of May 13, 2025; and (2) provide support to the Minister of Artificial Intelligence and Digital Innovation in the carrying out of that Minister's responsibilities.
